  "text": "In recent work, we have developed a gentle foaming facial cleanser utilizing HMP. The effects on the skin barrier following treatment with this formulation (NUG) compared to a leading dermatologist-recommended lotion facial cleanser (CGSC) were compared. With images obtained from multiphoton laser scanning confocal microscope [CITATION_1] , the benefits provided by HMP technology of minimizing the SC barrier disruption were visualized directly. The skin samples were mounted on a Franz diffusion cell with SC facing the donor chamber and cleansers, diluted with distilled water to a concentration of 80%, were applied and maintained at 37",
